name: Hello, My Name is Kristina
tagline: I create delightful experiences through website design!
body:
Welcome to My Page
      Good designs are not about fancy tricks and cutting-edge technology or
      trendy fads. It is all about communication and building brand integrity. I can build   
      you a webpage that uses layout, colors, fonts and imagery as well as icon design that
      will inspire your customers to continue reading, and to be repeat customers. The only thing
      that matters in this world is family and friends. Here in Wisconsin, we are world renowned
      for three things....The Green Bay Packers, cheese, and cows. Some people might get offended
      if you referred to them as a cheesehead. Not me. I always say, "I have been called a lot worse!"
